General.Name: Da Hui Limited
General.Description: Da Hui Limited produces and sells motorcycle components and child safety seats in the United States, Malaysia, and internationally. The company's Child Safety Seat segment manufactures and trades car seats. Its Motorcycle Component segment is involved in the manufacturing and trading of motorcycle components. The company also provides infant car seats, no back boosters, and big kid boosters; home safety baby gates; strollers; and accessories. In addition, the company offers lamp, speedometer, wire harness, and fuel level sender motor products. Further, the company engages in investment business. Da Hui Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
